Describe the feature or problem you’d like to solve
The OpenAI json spec has a parameter "runtimeHint" to tell the client what command to use when setting up the mcp server declaration from an MCP Registry.
Please update VSCode so that it honors this field.
My company uses Podman instead of Docker for container management locally and this seems like the way to change the docker command to a podman command.

Proposed solution
VSCode honors the runtimeHint parameter from the OpenAI spec so that I can set Podman as the image runner instead of Docker.

